data.description: Welcome to this inviting home nestled on a tranquil wooded cul-de-sac lot. Upon entry you will appreciate the open floor plan with custom crown moldings that add a touch of elegance. The spacious eat-in kitchen with breakfast bar seating offers a perfect setting for family gatherings, and it flows seamlessly into the inviting living area, complete with a fireplace and built-in surround sound for your entertainment needs. Work from home in the conveniently located office downstairs.  Step outside and enjoy the privacy of a fenced backyard with a sizable patio-a great spot for relaxation and outdoor activities. Head upstairs where the Owner's En-Suite plus 3 additional bedrooms and full bathroom are located. Spacious Owner's Suite offers a retreat from the stresses of the day. Myers Milloffers great amenities, a fantastic location close to shopping, restaurants, downtown Summerville, interstate and award winning DD2 schools.
